# Evolution

> How this hermit has changed over time.

## First Session
```dataview
TABLE task, cost_usd AS "Cost", duration, escalation
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/sessions"
WHERE id
SORT date ASC LIMIT 1
```

## Latest Session
```dataview
TABLE task, cost_usd AS "Cost", duration, escalation
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/sessions"
WHERE id
SORT date DESC LIMIT 1
```

## Cost by Week
```dataview
TABLE length(rows) AS "Sessions", round(sum(rows.cost_usd), 2) AS "Cost"
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/sessions"
WHERE id
GROUP BY dateformat(date, "yyyy-'W'WW") AS "Week"
SORT Week DESC
LIMIT 8
```

## Autonomy Over Time
<!-- operator_turns = 0: completed without operator redirection. Escalation: configured trust level. -->
```dataview
TABLE
  length(filter(rows, (r) => r.operator_turns = 0)) AS "Self-directed",
  length(filter(rows, (r) => r.operator_turns > 0)) AS "Assisted",
  length(rows) AS "Total",
  round(length(filter(rows, (r) => r.operator_turns = 0)) / length(rows) * 100) + "%" AS "Rate"
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/sessions"
WHERE id AND operator_turns != null
GROUP BY dateformat(date, "yyyy-'W'WW") AS "Week"
SORT Week DESC
LIMIT 8
```

## Proposal Resolution Time
```dataview
TABLE title,
  (date(resolved_date) - date(created)).days AS "Days to Resolve",
  resolved_date
FROM "{{HERMIT_PATH}}/proposals"
WHERE id AND status = "resolved" AND resolved_date
SORT resolved_date DESC
LIMIT 15
```

